Portugal contract six-year 150 mln ECU loan foreign bank lead Daiwa Europe Ltd finance investment project finance ministry said. Interest 7.75 pct paid annual instalment start 1988 ministry spokesman Luis Vilhena de Cunha said. The loan form temporary global note replace subscription 1000 10000 ECUs. The issue price 101.75 pct. Banque Generale du Luxembourg SA act listing agent fiscal agent spokesman added. REUTER 